Date: Wed, 23 Dec 2015 12:32:56 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Conform to PEP 0394 in Python sources

In order to tolerate differences across platforms, all new code that
needs to invoke the Python interpreter should not specify python,
but rather should specify either python2 or python3
---
 utils/lit/lit.py                                             | 2 +-
 utils/lit/lit/ProgressBar.py                                 | 2 +-
 utils/lit/lit/main.py                                        | 2 +-
 utils/lit/tests/Inputs/googletest-format/DummySubDir/OneTest | 2 +-
 4 files changed, 4 insertions(+), 4 deletions(-)

diff --git a/utils/lit/lit.py b/utils/lit/lit.py
index 851063b..680fdd7 100755
--- a/utils/lit/lit.py
+++ b/utils/lit/lit.py
@@ -1,4 +1,4 @@
-#!/usr/bin/env python
+#!/usr/bin/env python2
 
 if __name__=='__main__':
     import lit
diff --git a/utils/lit/lit/ProgressBar.py b/utils/lit/lit/ProgressBar.py
index 3ad704d..90e33fb 100644
--- a/utils/lit/lit/ProgressBar.py
+++ b/utils/lit/lit/ProgressBar.py
@@ -1,4 +1,4 @@
-#!/usr/bin/env python
+#!/usr/bin/env python2
 
 # Source: http://code.activestate.com/recipes/475116/, with
 # modifications by Daniel Dunbar.
diff --git a/utils/lit/lit/main.py b/utils/lit/lit/main.py
index 18c4a8c..5fb9a2e 100755
--- a/utils/lit/lit/main.py
+++ b/utils/lit/lit/main.py
@@ -1,4 +1,4 @@
-#!/usr/bin/env python
+#!/usr/bin/env python2
 
 """
 lit - LLVM Integrated Tester.
diff --git a/utils/lit/tests/Inputs/googletest-format/DummySubDir/OneTest b/utils/lit/tests/Inputs/googletest-format/DummySubDir/OneTest
index dd49f02..22dc7c5 100755
--- a/utils/lit/tests/Inputs/googletest-format/DummySubDir/OneTest
+++ b/utils/lit/tests/Inputs/googletest-format/DummySubDir/OneTest
@@ -1,4 +1,4 @@
